<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Preplings!</title>
    <style>
        /* Base styles - Tailwind-like */
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: #374151; /* gray-700 */
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #F3F4F6; /* gray-100 */
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
            -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
        }

        /* Container */
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #FFFFFF;
            border-radius: 0.5rem; /* rounded-lg */
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 2px 4px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); /* shadow-md */
        }

        /* Logo container */
        .logo-container {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 1.5rem 0 1rem 0;
        }

        .logo {
            max-width: 150px;
            height: auto;
        }

        /* Header */
        .header {
            background-color: #4A90E2; /* primary blue */
            padding: 1.5rem;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }

        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        /* Content */
        .content {
            padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
        }

        /* Message */
        .message {
            font-size: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        /* Button */
        .button-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 1.5rem 0;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #4A90E2; /* primary blue */
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 0.375rem; /* rounded-md */
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: background-color 0.2s;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background-color: #3A7BC8; /* darker blue */
        }

        /* Footer */
        .footer {
            background-color: #F9FAFB; /* gray-50 */
            padding: 1.25rem;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            color: #6B7280; /* gray-500 */
            border-top: 1px solid #E5E7EB; /* gray-200 */
        }

        /* Feature box */
        .feature-box {
            background-color: #F9FAFB; /* gray-50 */
            border: 1px solid #E5E7EB; /* gray-200 */
            border-radius: 0.5rem; /* rounded-lg */
            padding: 1.25rem;
            margin: 1.5rem 0;
        }

        .feature-title {
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
            color: #111827; /* gray-900 */
        }

        .feature-box ul {
            margin: 0;
            padding-left: 1.5rem;
        }

        .feature-box li {
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            position: relative;
        }

        .feature-box li::before {
            content: "â€¢";
            color: #4A90E2; /* primary blue */
            font-weight: bold;
            display: inline-block;
            width: 1rem;
            margin-left: -1rem;
        }

        /* Responsive adjustments */
        @media (max-width: 640px) {
            .container {
                border-radius: 0;
            }

            .content {
                padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="logo-container">
            <img src="https://preplings.com/logo.png" alt="Preplings Logo" class="logo">
        </div>
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Welcome to Preplings!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <div class="message">
                <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>
                <p>Congratulations on joining Preplings! We're thrilled to have you as part of our community of language learners.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-box">
                <div class="feature-title">Here's what you can do now:</div>
                <ul>
                    <li>Complete your profile and set your learning goals</li>
                    <li>Explore our language courses and learning resources</li>
                    <li>Start your first lesson and earn rewards</li>
                    <li>Connect with other language learners</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <p>Learning a new language is an exciting journey, and we're here to make it fun and effective for you!</p>
            <p>Happy learning,<br>The Preplings Team</p>

            <div class="button-container">
                <a href="<%= websiteUrl %>" class="button">Start Learning Now</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Preplings. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>If you have any questions, please contact our support team at <a href="mailto:care@preplings.com" style="color: #4A90E2; text-decoration: none;">care@preplings.com</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
